ason#Spring season}}\n\nDetails for the 2020 NISA Spring season were announced January 27, 2020.<ref>{{cite web |title=Schedule |url=https://www.nisaofficial.com/schedule |website=National Independent Soccer Association |accessdate=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==== Standings ====\n{{2020 NISA Spring standings}}\n\n==== Results summary ====\n{{Fb rs|hw=0|hd=0|hl=0|hgf=0|hga=0|aw=0|ad=0|al=2|agf=1|aga=3}}\n{{Fb rs footer|u=7 March 2020|s=[[#Match reports|Match reports]] |date=March 2020}}\n\n==== Matches ====\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round      = 1\n|date       = {{Start date|2020|02|29}}\n|time       = 7:00{{nbsp}}p.m.\n|team1      = [[California United Strikers FC]]\n|score      = 1\u20130\n|report     = [https://www.calunitedstrikers.com/news/2020/03/01/cal-united-strikers-v-michigan-stars-game-recap Report]<br>[https://mycujoo.tv/en/club/california-united-strikers-fc-j70rr3?id=90278&play=true&tvId=846 MyCujoo Broadcast]\n|team2      = [[Michigan Stars FC]]\n|goals1     =\n* [[Kevin Jeon|Jeon]] {{goal|59}}\n|goals2     =\n* [[Zachary Reynolds (soccer)|Reynolds]] {{yel|7}}\n* [[Patrick Sullivan (soccer)|Sullivan]] {{yel|23}}\n* [[Cameron Schneider|Schneider]] {{yel|82}}\n|stadium    = [[Orange County Great Park|Championship Soccer Stadium]]\n|location   = [[Irvine, California]]\n|attendance = 2,258\n|referee    = William Randy Hoffman\n|result     = L\n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round      = 2\n|date       = {{Start date|2020|03|07}}\n|time       = 5:10{{nbsp}}p.m.\n|team1      = [[Oakland Roots SC]]\n|score      = 2\u20131 \n|report     = [https://mycujoo.tv/en/video/oakland-roots-sc?id=ck5xzkif9r5940haiu3rpabat MyCujoo Broadcast]\n|team2      = [[Michigan Stars FC]]\n|goals1     = \n* [[Yohannes Harish|Harish]] {{yel|16}}\n* [[Nikolai Littleton|Littleton]] {{yel|45}}\n* [[Jack McInerney|McInerney]] {{goal|75|pen.}}\n* [[Alex Garuba|Garuba]] {{goal|82}}\n* [[Nana Attakora|Attakora]] {{yel|88}}\n|goals2     =\n* [[Zanin Mahic|Mahic]] {{yel|12}}\n* [[Cameron S