first1=Larry |title=Overhauled Michigan Stars shooting for tactical efficiency in jump to pro league |url=https://www.detroitnews.com/story/sports/soccer/2020/02/21/overhauled-michigan-stars-shooting-tactical-efficiency-jump-pro-league/4828053002/ |website=Detroit News |accessdate=21 March 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n\n==Club==\n\n=== Roster ===\n''As of March 11, 2020.''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.michiganstarsfc.com/roster |title=Michigan Stars FC Roster |accessdate=March 21, 2020}}</ref>\n<!----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  -- Do NOT add new players before their signing is officially announced by the club\n  -- and do NOT assign unreferenced squad numbers as well.\n  -- Players with international caps should NOT be bolded&nbsp;\u2013 as per Wikipedia:WikiProject_Football/Clubs\n &nbsp;\u2013 This is Wikipedia, not a football gazette.\n &nbsp;\u2013 Any unconfirmed and unsourced signing/transfer will be reverted at sight.\n &nbsp;\u2013 Thanks in advance.\n  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! {{Abbr|No.|Number}}\n! {{Abbr|Pos.|Position}}\n! {{Abbr|Nat.|Nationality}}\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | Name\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | Date of birth (age)\n! {{Abbr|Since|Contract since}}\n|-\n| 1 || [[Goalkeeper (association football)|GK]] || {{flagicon|IRN}} || data-sort-value=\"Aghababazadeh, Arshia\" style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Arshia Aghababazadeh]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | {{Birth date and age|1995|11|5}} || 2020\n|-\n| 2 || [[Defender (association football)|DF]] || {{flagicon|USA}} || data-sort-value=\"Lobsiger, Tekodah\" style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Tekodah Lobsiger]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | {{Birth date and age|1995|2|14}} || 2020\n|-\n| 3 || [[Defender (association football)|DF]] || {{flagicon|ISR}} || data-sort-value=\"Ben-Tal, Gonnie\" style